WEBVTT

00:02:28.225 --> 00:02:31.117
were extraordinarily proud of the work they did,

00:02:31.117 --> 00:02:33.117
and justifiably so.

00:02:33.117 --> 00:02:34.651
Some of the largest vessels

00:02:34.651 --> 00:02:36.579
ever constructed on planet Earth

00:02:36.579 --> 00:02:40.379
were built right at the end of my street.

00:02:40.379 --> 00:02:43.440
My grandfather had been a shipwright,

00:02:43.440 --> 00:02:44.777
and as a child,

00:02:44.777 --> 00:02:46.649
as there were few other jobs in the town,

00:02:46.649 --> 00:02:49.213
I would wonder with some anxiety

00:02:49.213 --> 00:02:52.371
whether that would be my destiny too.

00:02:52.371 --> 00:02:55.443
I was fairly determined that it wouldn't be.

00:02:55.443 --> 00:02:57.087
I had other dreams,

00:02:57.087 --> 00:02:59.589
not necessarily practical ones,

